{"tid":1500481,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"柯文哲:香港示威活動或國慶前「悲劇收場」","createTime":"2019-08-24T04:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T05:31:36.000Z","uid":58335,"like":2,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7637207732baa615698bddc42e6e3f90860c3e9c","tid":1500481,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:41:59.000Z","msg":"呢條奶共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n台北市長柯文哲周五接受台灣傳媒專訪時談及香港反修例示威。他估計，中國大陸應該會在10月1日國慶前解決香港問題，港人的示威活動很可能「悲劇收場」，但他未進一步闡述。<br />\n<br />\n柯文哲稱，根據他的看法，大陸已經要用上海與深圳取代香港，香港很快變為「一國一制」。他呼籲北京「要聰明一點，要慢慢Release(鬆綁)」。他認為，北京「做不做都不對」，「不管就是繼續亂，管了就是六四」，國家主席習近平往後退「一步就好，政治都在一念之間」。<br />\n<br />\n柯文哲又說，就算支持香港示威活動，也不用在媒體上講一大堆，更不需要挑釁對岸。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2229530/%E6%9F%AF%E6%96%87%E5%93%B2%3A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%88%96%E5%9C%8B%E6%85%B6%E5%89%8D%E3%80%8C%E6%82%B2%E5%8A%87%E6%94%B6%E5%A0%B4%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2229530%2F%25E6%259F%25AF%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%2593%25B2%253A%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2585%25B6%25E5%2589%258D%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%2582%25B2%25E5%258A%2587%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E3%2580%258D&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=fd278fb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2229530/%E6%9F%AF%E6%96%87%E5%93%B2%3A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%88%96%E5%9C%8B%E6%85%B6%E5%89%8D%E3%80%8C%E6%82%B2%E5%8A%87%E6%94%B6%E5%A0%B4%E3%80%8D</a>"},{"pid":"e9546b8dc060a489113d19c68fd049af720452d9","tid":1500481,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f20553406aab6e3cf665ef9217b27f3687d501b","tid":1500481,"uid":87780,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:46:22.000Z","msg":"台灣湯渣華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b5be0c0d07663b4e1c7b2d945c394002a9743c","tid":1500481,"uid":73340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T05:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ok明白<br />\n幫柯叔叔係台灣宣傳下先"},{"pid":"2172c997afaad3ef1c22eb16799add263100f6aa","tid":1500481,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T05:14:05.000Z","msg":"隔岸觀火<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e00f94092f195a1b68ec16ff81d6ee82616ef0e","tid":1500481,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T05:15:57.000Z","msg":"不管就真自治<br />\n管了就繼續亂"},{"pid":"d76bd3095f1f6feb1e50682ea7919f21d4ce5f88","tid":1500481,"uid":193215,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"9f20553406aab6e3cf665ef9217b27f3687d501b","tid":1500481,"uid":87780,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:46:22.000Z","msg":"台灣湯渣華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T05:16:04.000Z","msg":"形容得好貼切 我重諗緊用邊個比喻佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06e2ae8e238c555183c9c8f4dcb25ccca40b8b4","tid":1500481,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d76bd3095f1f6feb1e50682ea7919f21d4ce5f88","tid":1500481,"uid":193215,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"9f20553406aab6e3cf665ef9217b27f3687d501b","tid":1500481,"uid":87780,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:46:22.000Z